snippet: Former Barcelona and Argentina defender Gabriel Milito has quit as coach of Independiente after Saturday’s 1-0 home defeat by Banfield in the Argentine first division....
lead_paragraph: Former Barcelona and Argentina defender Gabriel Milito has quit as coach of Independiente after Saturday’s 1-0 home defeat by Banfield in the Argentine first division.

headline.main: Milito Leaves Independiente as Argentine Coaching Exodus Continues
headline.print_headline: Milito Leaves Independiente as Argentine Coaching Exodus Continues
